{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, boom, as I backed away, the third shot hit right in that swirl of water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- [LAUGHS] so of course, we reported by radio, and about four destroyers converged on Tinian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in about an hour, I got the word, it's safe now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you ever try to pick up-- you've probably never tried to pick up a slipped anchor-- woo-hoo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, we did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was a pain the ass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- now where the hell was I?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, you were in San Diego.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm wondering, when you're in San Diego and the Japanese surrender, what happens next to you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- yeah, they decided-- now this is on-- I'm on the roper now, this old four-piper that had been damaged by the kamikaze.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the question was, were they going to spend time and the Navy's money fixing up this old four-piper that was 20-odd years old at this point, or just scrap it and send a new ship, see?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent a-- a Navy Board of Inspection and Survey on board to decide this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was headed by an admiral, and the second in command was a Captain, and they had a third, a commander, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a-- I was a Lieutenant in all my glory-- two big stripes, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] and-- and so anyway, they all-- I thought I had a good-- I know I had a good ship, a very good ship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was walking-- after all-- everybody who was supposed to make these inspections, they would come back and report to the admiral.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was walking with admiral, pacing back and forth on my deck, waiting for these reports to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
